                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>keracunan / mabuk</p><p><strong>Penjelasan:</strong></p><p>karena terdapat alkohol yang berbahaya bagi tubuh manusia .</p><p><strong>TOLONG</strong><strong> </strong><strong>FOLLOW</strong><strong> </strong><strong>AND</strong><strong> </strong><strong>BERI</strong><strong> </strong><strong>RATTING</strong><strong> </strong><strong>+</strong><strong> </strong><strong>KOMENTAR</strong><strong> </strong><strong>.</strong><strong>JIKA</strong><strong> </strong><strong>ADA</strong><strong> </strong><strong>KESALAHAN</strong><strong> </strong><strong>MOHOM</strong><strong> </strong><strong>MAAF</strong><strong> </strong></p><p></p><br />
